div.div:
1) Minimizer
update_score() ->
fille state metadata with top rated testcase indices
Top rated testcases are determined based on trace length and execution time.
Top rated testcases contain a map from "map index" -> "corpus index"
Look up all "better/shorter" testcases which visited the same indices and add them to top rated testcases.
Determines for each visited code node the "best" testcase
cull() ->
mark top rated testcases as favored
next() ->
Gets favored testcases or non-fav testcases with smaller probability (non-fav testcases are skipped with 95% propability)
Generic M = List of visted indices
TopRatedsMetadata -> state
IfFavoredMetadata -> Testcase
